title: Agricultural Drainage Well Buffers, Iowa, 1991
name: Agricultural Drainage Well Buffers, Iowa, 1991
description:
Abstract:

Agricultural drainage wells were located to 1/4, 1/4 sections  and locations were calculated from the registered location. This coverage was created by putting a 400 meter buffer around all of the points in ADW.

Purpose:

This digital, geographically referenced data set was developed by the Iowa Department of Natural Resources to carry out agency responsibilities related to management, protection, and development of Iowa's natural resources.
